These files were originally licensed under GPLv2 or later. For compatibility
with the rest of the Sunela project, they are now dual-licensed under the MIT
License as well.


Bouffalo SDK
------------

The sdk/ directory of the firmware contains the following files from the HID
example (bouffalo_sdk/examples/peripherals/usbdev/usbd_hid_keyboard/) of the
Bouffalo SDK: CMakeLists.txt Makefile flash_prog_cfg.ini proj.conf usb_config.h

With the exception of usb_config.h, all files were modified for the Sunela
project. Furthermore, sdk-main.c is based on main.c and sdk-usb.c is based on hid_keyboard_template.c

The Bouffalo SDK is licensed under the Apache 2.0 license. See LICENSE.Apache
for a copy of the license.


